data.description: Welcome to this charming all brick 3 bed 2 bath home. This well-maintained property features a spacious living area, a modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances, and a cozy backyard perfect for entertaining. The owner suite offers a relaxing retreat, while the remaining bedrooms provide ample space.  The home is conveniently located near Fort Stewart and close to shopping!
